13 pages, uuencoded compressed postscript file including one figure;
  contribution to the proceedings of the 5th annual astrophysics conference in
  Maryland on Dark Matter, 10 - 12 October, 1994

column11:
  A new upper bound is given for the dimension of the space of holomorphic cusp
forms of weight one and prime level $q$: $$ \hbox{dim}\, S_1(q) << q^{11/12}
\log^4{q} $$ with an absolute implied constant.
